      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am absolutely thrilled to list my pride and joy! This beauty is in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been pampered since day one, kept in a garage, and the interior still has that fresh car smell! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, you\u2019ve found it. Come see it for yourself; I promise you\u2019ll fall in love! \u2728",
