    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six. This specimen boasts a meticulously maintained double VANOS system and individual throttle bodies for razor-sharp throttle response. The 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, free of synchro wear. Crucially, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the M-Variable limited-slip differential operates silently. The suspension geometry remains true, benefiting from a recent overhaul of the control arm bushings and dampers. With original paint depth and all factory VIN stickers intact, this is a mechanically flawless example of BMW's finest naturally aspirated era.",
